the Settlement House movement. Settlement Houses originated in the late 1800s with the goal of promoting social and economic equity for new immigrants through education, social services, community organizing, and community building.', '', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '73-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-06-30 23:35:33', '2014-06-30 23:35:33', '', 73, 'http://www.sfnct.org/73-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
